<li>Thinking of your family with heartfelt sorrow. May memories of your aunt bring you comfort.</li>
<li>I was so saddened to hear of your aunt's passing.  She was a wonderful woman.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincerest condolences on the loss of your beloved aunt.</li>
<li>Your aunt's kindness and warmth will always be remembered.  May her memory be a blessing.</li>
<li>We are keeping your family in our thoughts and prayers.</li>
